Marigold restaurant has the most delectable authentic north Indian food. Being the first Indian restaurant in the village of Franschhoek, Marigold made sure to be open on this year’s Bastille weekend on July 15 and 16. While the restaurant won’t have a presence in the Bastille Day tent the restaurant has already received bookings for the weekend. Seasoned chef Vanie Padayachee takes us through some of their menu items in the video below: 